T02TD2285E:142b-1: aa mri ta siddhi m'u la n'a ma /
T02TD2285E:142b-3: bdud rtsi grub pa'i rtsa ba zhes bya ba /
T02TD2285E:142b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2285E:142b-5: spyan gsum rab ldan dbu bcas sku mdog dmar //
T02TD2285E:143a-0: @143a * // 'chi ba'i 'jigs sel rnal 'byor pho mo yi //
T02TD2285E:143a-1: phyag rgya 'dzin cing birwa ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2285E:143a-2: skyob mdzad phyag rgya'i zhabs la bdag 'dud do //
T02TD2285E:143a-3: phyag rgya chen po rnams bshad bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-4: mi ni gang gis thos pa la //
T02TD2285E:143a-5: lha rnams kun gyis bkur sti mdzad //
T02TD2285E:143a-6: skye ba bye ba stong dag tu //
T02TD2285E:143a-7: legs las rgya chen rnams byas pas //
T02TD2285E:143a-8: de thob 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho la //
T02TD2285E:143a-10: g-yon pa'i rting pas bshang lam dgag / g-yas pa cung zad brkyang byas la //
T02TD2285E:143a-11: mtheb chen bol gong lag pas gzung //
T02TD2285E:143a-12: snying ga lkog mas mnan pa ni //
T02TD2285E:143a-13: sgo dgu dgag pa'i sbyor ba'o //
T02TD2285E:143a-14: de yi rtsa gsum dag la ni //
T02TD2285E:143a-15: rim pa bzhin du bsnun par bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-17: rkang pa gcig pa sems bsdu zhing //
T02TD2285E:143a-18: rlung rnams gcig tu bsdus bya ste //
T02TD2285E:143a-19: rlung gis bsdam pa brtsam par bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-20: nyi zla gnyis ni gcig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-21: de ltar byas na rlung ni 'gag /'di ni dam tshig phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2285E:143a-22: bshang lam 'khor lo gyen du bzlog / thig le sgra bcas gyen du bslang //
T02TD2285E:143a-23: rtsa rnams thams cad rab tu g-yo //
T02TD2285E:143a-24: mchog gi rtsa ni gyen du 'ong //
T02TD2285E:143a-25: lus ngag yid gsum sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2285E:143a-26: sku gsung thugs ni bsgrub par bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-27: goms pa brtan par gyur pa yis //
T02TD2285E:143a-28: rang gi me ni gsal ba'o //
T02TD2285E:143a-29: phyag rgya 'di yis thams cad du //
T02TD2285E:143a-31: 'di ni kha sbyor sbyor ba ste ;
T02TD2285E:143a-33: 'di ni rlung gi sbyor ba yin //
T02TD2285E:143a-34: mkhas pa rnams kyis 'di bsgrub po //
T02TD2285E:143a-35: phyag rgya gnyis su shes par bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-36: ji bzhin bsdam pa'i cho ga shes //
T02TD2285E:143a-37: dzo ni lha mo'i phyag rgya yin //
T02TD2285E:143a-38: ling+ga'i phyag rgya lha yin no //
T02TD2285E:143a-39: pho dang mo yi sbyor ba las //
T02TD2285E:143a-40: phyi rol du ni skyes pa 'byung //
T02TD2285E:143a-41: ji bzhin sbyor ba 'di gnyis kyis //
T02TD2285E:143a-42: skye ba nang du gsang bar bya //
T02TD2285E:143a-43: rtsa ni bud med gzugs can te //
T02TD2285E:143a-44: skyes pa med na 'bras bu med //
T02TD2285E:143a-45: phyag rgya che dang bsdams pa che //
T02TD2285E:143a-46: dbye ba med na 'bras bu med //
T02TD2285E:143b-0: rlung ni @143b 'khor lo gcig tu bsdu //
T02TD2285E:143b-1: ji srid bsdams pa bzhin du bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-2: rnal 'byor ba yis bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-3: rang gi rlung sems bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-4: sbyor ba'i rim pas bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-5: rlung ni stobs dang ldan byas la //
T02TD2285E:143b-6: dbu ma'i sgo ru gzhug bya ste //
T02TD2285E:143b-7: 'khor lo bzhi po rlung gis dbug / lag gnyis ling+ga'i phyag rgya bca' //
T02TD2285E:143b-8: de ni sa la gzhag nas su //
T02TD2285E:143b-9: rkang pa'i tse mos la gzugs //
T02TD2285E:143b-10: brla ni brdab par bya ba yis //
T02TD2285E:143b-11: rlung gis rlung ni bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-12: rlung gis rlung la bteg par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-13: rlung gis rlung ni gsad par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-14: rlung gis yongs la khyab pa yis //
T02TD2285E:143b-15: rlung gis dngos grub thams cad sbyin //
T02TD2285E:143b-17: des ni bdud rtsi grub par ni //
T02TD2285E:143b-18: bi rwa nga yis yang dag bshad //
T02TD2285E:143b-19: legs par bsdams pa lus kyi las //
T02TD2285E:143b-20: rdo rje rlung rtse bye ba yis //
T02TD2285E:143b-21: lhun po yi ni bar dag tu //
T02TD2285E:143b-22: dgug pa'i sbyor ba 'di yis ni //
T02TD2285E:143b-23: tshangs sogs mdud pa bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-24: lhun po'i steng du lha rnams 'gro //
T02TD2285E:143b-25: lhun po dag ni g-yo 'gyur te //
T02TD2285E:143b-26: des ni thams cad brgyal bar 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:143b-27: tshangs pa la sogs lha rnams bsad //
T02TD2285E:143b-28: dang po yi ni sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2285E:143b-29: tshangs pa'i mdud pa bshig par bya //
T02TD2285E:143b-30: de nas dbang phyug mdud pa bshig / de bshig nas ni bishnu bshig / de nas gti mug la sogs spangs //
T02TD2285E:143b-31: gtsug tor sgo ni sbas pa la //
T02TD2285E:143b-32: rlung gis sgo ni rnam par dbye //
T02TD2285E:143b-34: bsdam pa che dang 'bigs pa che ;
T02TD2285E:143b-35: ; phyag rgya che ni gsum pa yin //
T02TD2285E:143b-36: 'di ni gsang dbang gsum yin no //
T02TD2285E:143b-37: 'di dag gis na sbyor grub grags //
T02TD2285E:143b-38: de nyid gsum ni gang rig pas //
T02TD2285E:143b-39: de ni 'jig rten gsum rig go //
T02TD2285E:143b-40: gang gis 'di la goms byas na //
T02TD2285E:143b-41: thams cad kyi ni mnga' bdag 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:143b-42: gsang ba lha yi lha rnams dang //
T02TD2285E:143b-43: mi yi bdag po'i bdag por 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:143b-44: dbang bskur kun la dbang ba yin //
T02TD2285E:143b-45: thams cad ma lus lhag par 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:143b-46: des na lha rnams kun gyi dbang //
T02TD2285E:143b-48: phyag rgya che la goms par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-2: grub pa chen po 'byung ba yin //
T02TD2285E:144a-3: phyag rgya chen po gang yin pa //
T02TD2285E:144a-4: rnam gnyis de ni dam pa dang //
T02TD2285E:144a-5: 'chi ba las ni grol ba dang //
T02TD2285E:144a-6: lus sems dag la bde ba 'byung //
T02TD2285E:144a-7: sems la gnas pa tsam gyis kyang //
T02TD2285E:144a-8: mngal du skye bar mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD2285E:144a-9: dang po'i ming ni yi ge yin //
T02TD2285E:144a-10: sbyor ba ldan pa bshad par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-11: dad dang ldan pa'i sbyor ba yin //
T02TD2285E:144a-12: rnal 'byor pa ni nges par ni //
T02TD2285E:144a-13: phyag rgya chen po 'grub pa yin //
T02TD2285E:144a-14: phyag rgya chen po bshad par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-15: rkang pa lag pa bsdam bya ste //
T02TD2285E:144a-16: rlung ni lan gsum 'thungs byas la //
T02TD2285E:144a-17: rtsa rnams thams cad 'then par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-18: langs pas rtsa rnams gyen du phyogs //
T02TD2285E:144a-19: nad rnams thams cad bcom nas ni //
T02TD2285E:144a-20: phyag rgya chen po'i don yang rdzogs //
T02TD2285E:144a-21: ji ltar nam mkha' bar snang la //
T02TD2285E:144a-23: ; rlung gi shugs kyis gtor ba ltar //
T02TD2285E:144a-24: de ltar lus 'di dag la ni //
T02TD2285E:144a-25: nad kyis yongs su bsgos gyur kyang //
T02TD2285E:144a-26: thabs kyi rlung gis gzhom par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-28: dzha ye dha yi karma yi //
T02TD2285E:144a-29: lag pas 'byung ba lnga dag kyang //
T02TD2285E:144a-30: las kyi bya bas mnye bya zhing ;
T02TD2285E:144a-31: / bsdams pa chen pos gnas pa yi //
T02TD2285E:144a-33: steng du lha yi 'jig rten skrag / lag pa brkyang bskum 'di yis ni //
T02TD2285E:144a-34: phyogs bzhi dag kyang g-yo bar byed //
T02TD2285E:144a-35: rkang pa 'og tu brkyang pa yis //
T02TD2285E:144a-36: klu rnams thams cad skrag par byed//
T02TD2285E:144a-37: dbang po ngal zhing dub ba'i tshe //
T02TD2285E:144a-38: rtse gcig sems kyi ngang las gzhag / bsdam pa'i sbyor ba bshad par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-40: bsdam pa gnyis ni shes bya ste //
T02TD2285E:144a-41: ji ltar thig le gnas pa dang //
T02TD2285E:144a-42: dzo ni bha dha'i lha mo yin //
T02TD2285E:144a-43: mgrin pa bsdams pa lha yin no //
T02TD2285E:144a-44: dgang ba can dang bum pa can //
T02TD2285E:144a-45: phyag rgya gzung ba rnam par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-46: lha dang lha min kun la gsang //
T02TD2285E:144a-47: rnal 'byor bsdam par bya ba yis //
T02TD2285E:144a-48: dbu ma'i sgo gu gtad par bya //
T02TD2285E:144a-49: lam gsum rnam par bkag byas la //
T02TD2285E:144a-50: rlung ni nang du gzung bar bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-0: srog ni @144b rlung yang rlan par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-2: skad cig nyid la bsdam par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-3: steng 'og rlung gi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2285E:144b-4: mnyam pa'i rlung dang bsreg par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-5: des ni gyen du bskyod par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-6: bshang lam bsdams pa dang ldan pas //
T02TD2285E:144b-7: rlung ni rnam par bskum pa dang //
T02TD2285E:144b-8: gyen du blang ba byas pa yin //
T02TD2285E:144b-10: dgram dang rab tu bsdam par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-11: zung 'jug lam gsum bsgom par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-12: 'di ltar mi yi lus la ni //
T02TD2285E:144b-13: grub pa'i lam ni rab gsal ba //
T02TD2285E:144b-14: nyams myong skye zhing lus rgyas 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:144b-15: rgas par yang ni mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD2285E:144b-16: rtsa rnams rgyun gyis 'bab pa dang //
T02TD2285E:144b-18: bsdams pa chen po 'di yis ni //
T02TD2285E:144b-19: rnam par ldog par 'gyur ba yin //
T02TD2285E:144b-20: gshis ni thur du 'gro ba yin //
T02TD2285E:144b-21: yur ba'i nang du chu 'bab pa ;
T02TD2285E:144b-22: / de ni bsdams pas ldog par 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:144b-23: de bzhin nang gi lus la yang //
T02TD2285E:144b-24: lus kyi phyi rol 'gro ba de //
T02TD2285E:144b-25: rnal 'byor rtag tu shes par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-26: lus kyi rtsa ni ma lus pa //
T02TD2285E:144b-27: 'dis ni bsdams par rab tu grags //
T02TD2285E:144b-28: bsdams pa 'di yi mthu yis ni //
T02TD2285E:144b-29: lha rnams kun kyang gsal bar 'gyur //
T02TD2285E:144b-30: de ltar phyag rgya bzhi yis ni //
T02TD2285E:144b-31: lam gsum rnam par bkag pa'o //
T02TD2285E:144b-32: lam gcig pa ni gsal ba'o //
T02TD2285E:144b-33: grub pa lha yi lam du 'gro //
T02TD2285E:144b-34: skye dang 'chi ba'i lam gnyis po //
T02TD2285E:144b-35: 'og ni lam du bshad pa yin//
T02TD2285E:144b-36: bsod nams dang ni sdig rgyu yi //
T02TD2285E:144b-37: de phyir skyon gnyis rnam par spangs //
T02TD2285E:144b-38: rlung gi de nyid bum pa can //
T02TD2285E:144b-39: de ni rab tu mnyam par bya //
T02TD2285E:144b-40: steng gi lam du rnam byas la //
T02TD2285E:144b-41: rlung dang lhan cig sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2285E:144b-42: bsdams pas chu rgyun 'gag pa ltar //
T02TD2285E:144b-43: 'gro ba thams cad rnam par 'gog / des na de yi bka' drin gyis //
T02TD2285E:144b-44: dzo ni gdams pa zhes grags so //
T02TD2285E:144b-45: grub pa'i lam dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD2285E:144b-46: mi ni 'gyur te gzhan du min //
T02TD2285E:144b-47: phyag rgya 'di ni shes pa yis //
T02TD2285E:144b-48: dregs pa yod kyang don dang ldan //
T02TD2285E:144b-49: des na thams cad shes pa yin//
T02TD2285E:145a-0: @145a * // bdud rtsi grub pa zhes bya ba slob dpon chen po bi r'u pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2285E:145a-2: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po rnal 'byor pa las grub pa thob pa'i rgya gar ae de bas bsgyur ba'o//
